        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 2 min</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving – this is your <strong>green pea rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
